    "updated_at": "2013-09-12T02:04:55Z",
    "body": "After much hacking and testing, I think setting custom radii on windows is just too much hassle, and not really worth the effort. Instead, I updated the `rounded-corners` branch to simply round the top of the window to match the bottom for consistency. It should still be checked over, and merged. I'mma close this issue and open the branch as a PR for further discussion.\n"
